item.title: Call For Speakers
item.description: CFP is OPEN! Calling all Speakers and Presenters to submit a presentation here! Without presenters, a conference is just a bunch of nerds milling about without any central topics to discuss and learn about - it falls flat. If you’re curious about presenting but are unsure, come talk to us on Slack and we’ll sort it out! The CFP Formally closes on Feb 1st, 2025. Presentation FAQ: Speaker Qualifications What education level is required?
